{"captainVersion":4,"caproverOneClickApp":{"instructions":{"start":"Company Stores (Solidus) with PostgreSQL.\n\nDeploys the Company Stores e-commerce platform with a dedicated\nPostgreSQL instance hosting both the primary application database\nand the Solid Queue database. A separate worker container runs the\nbackground job processor (./bin/jobs).","end":"Your Company Stores app is now deployed.\n\n**Access:**\n- Storefront: https://$$cap_appname.$$cap_root_domain/\n- Admin:      https://$$cap_appname.$$cap_root_domain/admin/login\n\n**What was created:**\n- Web service:  $$cap_appname (Puma + Thruster, port 80)\n- Jobs service: $$cap_appname-jobs (Solid Queue worker)\n- Database:     $$cap_appname-db (Postgres, hosts both primary and queue DBs)\n\nSecrets such as SMTP credentials, Stripe keys, and Portal API keys\nfall through to config/credentials.yml.enc when their env vars are\nunset. RAILS_MASTER_KEY is required for that fallback to work."},"displayName":"Company Stores (Solidus + PostgreSQL)","isOfficial":false,"description":"Company Stores e-commerce platform (Solidus + Solid Queue) with bundled PostgreSQL and a dedicated job worker.","variables":[{"id":"$$cap_app_image","label":"App Image","defaultValue":"company_stores:latest","description":"Docker image for the app. Pin to a specific tag for production (e.g. company_stores:1.2.0) instead of :latest.","validRegex":"/^.+$/"},{"id":"$$cap_postgres_version","label":"PostgreSQL Version","defaultValue":"17.7","description":"PostgreSQL image tag (e.g. 17.7, 17). See https://hub.docker.com/_/postgres/tags for available tags.","validRegex":"/^([^\\s\\/])+$/"},{"id":"$$cap_db_user","label":"Database User","defaultValue":"solidus","description":"PostgreSQL username (used by both web and jobs containers, owns both DBs)","validRegex":"/^([a-zA-Z0-9_])+$/"},{"id":"$$cap_db_password","label":"Database Password","defaultValue":"$$cap_gen_random_hex(16)","description":"PostgreSQL password (auto-generated if left default)","validRegex":"/.{1,}/"},{"id":"$$cap_db_name","label":"Primary Database Name","defaultValue":"company_stores","description":"PostgreSQL database name for the application's primary connection","validRegex":"/^([a-zA-Z0-9_])+$/"},{"id":"$$cap_queue_db_name","label":"Queue Database Name","defaultValue":"company_stores_queue","description":"PostgreSQL database name for Solid Queue (separate from primary). Auto-created by the web container's db:prepare on first boot.","validRegex":"/^([a-zA-Z0-9_])+$/"},{"id":"$$cap_rails_master_key","label":"Rails Master Key","defaultValue":"","description":"Rails master key for decrypting config/credentials.yml.enc. REQUIRED. Get this from config/master.key in the source repo or your secret manager.","validRegex":"/.{32,}/"},{"id":"$$cap_job_concurrency","label":"Job Worker Processes","defaultValue":"1","description":"Number of Solid Queue worker processes inside the jobs container. Increase for higher throughput (each process uses ~150-300 MB).","validRegex":"/^[0-9]+$/"},{"id":"$$cap_smtp_address","label":"SMTP Address (optional)","defaultValue":"","description":"SMTP server host. Leave empty to fall back to credentials.yml.enc.","validRegex":"/.*/"},{"id":"$$cap_smtp_port","label":"SMTP Port (optional)","defaultValue":"","description":"SMTP port (e.g. 587). Leave empty to fall back to credentials.yml.enc.","validRegex":"/^[0-9]*$/"},{"id":"$$cap_smtp_username","label":"SMTP Username (optional)","defaultValue":"","description":"SMTP username. Leave empty to fall back to credentials.yml.enc.","validRegex":"/.*/"},{"id":"$$cap_smtp_password","label":"SMTP Password (optional)","defaultValue":"","description":"SMTP password. Leave empty to fall back to credentials.yml.enc.","validRegex":"/.*/"},{"id":"$$cap_smtp_domain","label":"SMTP Domain (optional)","defaultValue":"","description":"SMTP HELO domain. Leave empty to fall back to credentials.yml.enc.","validRegex":"/.*/"},{"id":"$$cap_smtp_authentication","label":"SMTP Authentication (optional)","defaultValue":"","description":"SMTP auth method (plain, login, cram_md5). Leave empty to fall back to credentials.yml.enc.","validRegex":"/^(plain|login|cram_md5|)$/"},{"id":"$$cap_mailer_host","label":"Mailer Host","defaultValue":"$$cap_appname.$$cap_root_domain","description":"Host used in mailer URLs (e.g. yourstore.com).","validRegex":"/.+/"},{"id":"$$cap_rails_log_level","label":"Rails Log Level","defaultValue":"info","description":"Rails log level (debug, info, warn, error, fatal)","validRegex":"/^(debug|info|warn|error|fatal)$/"},{"id":"$$cap_assume_ssl","label":"Assume SSL","defaultValue":"true","description":"Treat connections as HTTPS even when forwarded as HTTP (required when CapRover terminates TLS at the proxy).","validRegex":"/^(true|false)$/"},{"id":"$$cap_force_ssl","label":"Force SSL","defaultValue":"true","description":"Redirect HTTP to HTTPS at the Rails layer.","validRegex":"/^(true|false)$/"}]},"services":{"$$cap_appname-db":{"image":"postgres:$$cap_postgres_version","restart":"always","environment":{"POSTGRES_USER":"$$cap_db_user","POSTGRES_PASSWORD":"$$cap_db_password","POSTGRES_DB":"$$cap_db_name"},"volumes":["$$cap_appname-db-data:/var/lib/postgresql/data"],"caproverExtra":{"notExposeAsWebApp":"true"}},"$$cap_appname":{"image":"$$cap_app_image","restart":"always","depends_on":["$$cap_appname-db"],"environment":{"DATABASE_URL":"postgres://$$cap_db_user:$$cap_db_password@srv-captain--$$cap_appname-db:5432/$$cap_db_name","QUEUE_DATABASE_URL":"postgres://$$cap_db_user:$$cap_db_password@srv-captain--$$cap_appname-db:5432/$$cap_queue_db_name","RAILS_MASTER_KEY":"$$cap_rails_master_key","SMTP_ADDRESS":"$$cap_smtp_address","SMTP_PORT":"$$cap_smtp_port","SMTP_USERNAME":"$$cap_smtp_username","SMTP_PASSWORD":"$$cap_smtp_password","SMTP_DOMAIN":"$$cap_smtp_domain","SMTP_AUTHENTICATION":"$$cap_smtp_authentication","MAILER_HOST":"$$cap_mailer_host","RAILS_LOG_LEVEL":"$$cap_rails_log_level","ASSUME_SSL":"$$cap_assume_ssl","FORCE_SSL":"$$cap_force_ssl"},"caproverExtra":{"containerHttpPort":"80","websocketSupport":"false"},"volumes":["$$cap_appname-storage:/rails/storage"]},"$$cap_appname-jobs":{"image":"$$cap_app_image","restart":"always","depends_on":["$$cap_appname-db","$$cap_appname"],"environment":{"DATABASE_URL":"postgres://$$cap_db_user:$$cap_db_password@srv-captain--$$cap_appname-db:5432/$$cap_db_name","QUEUE_DATABASE_URL":"postgres://$$cap_db_user:$$cap_db_password@srv-captain--$$cap_appname-db:5432/$$cap_queue_db_name","RAILS_MASTER_KEY":"$$cap_rails_master_key","JOB_CONCURRENCY":"$$cap_job_concurrency","SMTP_ADDRESS":"$$cap_smtp_address","SMTP_PORT":"$$cap_smtp_port","SMTP_USERNAME":"$$cap_smtp_username","SMTP_PASSWORD":"$$cap_smtp_password","SMTP_DOMAIN":"$$cap_smtp_domain","SMTP_AUTHENTICATION":"$$cap_smtp_authentication","MAILER_HOST":"$$cap_mailer_host","RAILS_LOG_LEVEL":"$$cap_rails_log_level"},"command":["./bin/jobs"],"caproverExtra":{"notExposeAsWebApp":"true"},"volumes":["$$cap_appname-storage:/rails/storage"]}}}
